# will see the following message at the end:
#		"End of archive 1 (of 2)."
# Contents:  README MANIFEST COPYING comp.c graphics.c menu.h move.c
#   reversi.c
# Wrapped by billr@saab on Fri Oct 23 08:35:19 1992
